<Grid
  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
<Grid.RowDefinitions>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
    </Grid.RowDefinitions>
    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="10"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
	<!--TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Text="1985-8-18" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}"/-->
	<TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}">
		<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTime.Year}"/>-<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTime.Month, StringFormat={}{0:00}}"/>-<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTime.Day, StringFormat={}{0:00}}"/>
	</TextBlock>
    <!--TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Right" Text="05:00Z (06:00L)" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}"/-->
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Right" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}">
		<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTime.Hour, StringFormat={}{0:00}}"/>:<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTime.Minute, StringFormat={}{0:00}}"/>Z (<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTimeLocal.Hour, StringFormat={}{0:00}}"/>:<Run Text="{Binding MissionStartTimeLocal.Minute, StringFormat={}{0:00}}"/>L)
	</TextBlock>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="FROM:"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="COM 7TH OPERATIONAL SQUADRON (SF)"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="TO:"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="COM 2ND COASTAL DEFENSE DIVISION"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="SUBJ:"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="CONTACT REPORT - MISSION ORDER"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="4" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="#0-144.142.143"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="9" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" TextWrapping="Wrap">
      1. TACTICAL SITUATION: American submarines continue to attempt to infiltrate our bastion in the Barents Sea. 2nd Coastal Defense Division is charged with anti-submarine action against the Americans in our territorial sea. This morning, one of our attack submarines reported American acoustic signature approximately 150nm north of Ostrovnoy.
      <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
      2. PRIMARY OBJECTIVE: 2nd Coastal Division Detachment ANTON will move to last reported point of contact and destroy the American. 
      <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  3. FRIENDLY FORCES: Ka-25 is available for air support. Due to long overwater flight required to reach you, he is only loaded with sonobuoys.
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
	  4. ENEMY FORCES: K-481 is reporting signature correlating to USA STURGEON class attack submarine.
      <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
      5. WEAPON RELEASE: Authorized on all submarine contacts.
      <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
      6. EMCON: No restrictions.
	  <LineBreak/>
      <LineBreak/>
      6. REMARK: The American attack submarine is a dangerous enemy and must not be underestimated. Good luck, Comrades.
    </TextBlock>
</Grid>